        <div class="col-lg-8">
          <h2>Features</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Store the files in <strong>your own file system or use your AWS S3 account</strong>.</li>
            <li><strong>Auto-destruction of the files</strong> after a given amount of time.</li>
            <li><strong>Tag your uploaded files</strong> to efficiently look for them.</li>
            <li>Delete link, image resizing, search by tags and many more.</li>
          <ul>
        </div>
      </div>
